=The Empress Dowager On A Second Spring=

21
00:01:06,640 --> 00:01:07,520
Let's talk this out.

22
00:01:08,079 --> 00:01:08,736
Let her go.

23
00:01:09,640 --> 00:01:10,799
Zhao Chengtian, put it down!

24
00:01:11,799 --> 00:01:12,319
Calm down.

25
00:01:13,159 --> 00:01:13,952
Whatever you want.

26
00:01:16,599 --> 00:01:17,792
Even if I die today,

27
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:21,376
I'll take you with me.

28
00:01:22,519 --> 00:01:25,200
We'll be lovers in the underworld.

29
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,120
Uncle.

30
00:01:30,200 --> 00:01:31,000
Drop the blades.

31
00:01:31,400 --> 00:01:32,120
Drop them!

32
00:01:35,959 --> 00:01:37,632
I've waited so long for this day

33
00:01:38,920 --> 00:01:41,200
to finally wed you honorably.

34
00:01:42,120 --> 00:01:42,848
But all of you

35
00:01:45,040 --> 00:01:46,760
have ruined it!

36
00:01:47,799 --> 00:01:49,519
The Empress Dowager has long been mine.

37
00:01:50,200 --> 00:01:51,680
She even bore me a child.

38
00:01:53,000 --> 00:01:55,296
None of you shall take her from me!

39
00:01:56,239 --> 00:01:57,728
