184
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,200
You...

185
00:10:48,960 --> 00:10:51,008
But I remember
all the crucial things, don't I?

186
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:57,664
Rong,

187
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,039
