203
00:11:32,559 --> 00:11:34,759
As the Emperor's uncle?

204
00:11:36,000 --> 00:11:36,960
Yeah.

205
00:11:38,240 --> 00:11:38,656
Wait,

206
00:11:39,679 --> 00:11:41,120
